   "end": "6.320", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.200", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.960", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich finde es gut, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.560", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir heute \u00fcber dieses Thema diskutieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.040", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Denn die Versorgung pflegebed\u00fcrftiger Menschen stellt eine Herausforderung f\u00fcr unsere Gesellschaft dar, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.920", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und sie wird uns auch in den n\u00e4chsten Jahren immer wieder besch\u00e4ftigen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.920", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Menschen in Deutschland werden dank unserer guten Gesundheitsversorgung\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.320", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gott sei Dank\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.720", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "immer \u00e4lter. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.600", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber im Alter besteht eben auch das Risiko, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.800", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "pflegebed\u00fcrftig und krank zu werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.800", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.560", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "da bin ich mit fast allen meiner Vorredner einig\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.080", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ben\u00f6tigen wir dringend ein Sofortprogramm in allen Bereichen der Pflege."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.600", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Verbindliche Personalschl\u00fcssel sind w\u00fcnschenswert und werden von uns auf jeden Fall unterst\u00fctzt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.240", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Problem aber ist\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.880", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das wurde bisher von niemandem angesprochen\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.120", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Pflegekr\u00e4fte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.800", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die man braucht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.680", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um die Personalschl\u00fcssel zu erreichen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.240", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auf dem jetzigen Arbeitsmarkt \u00fcberhaupt nicht vorhanden sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.440", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist doch das Problem, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.400", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und da m\u00fcssen wir zuerst ansetzen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.800", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unsere hochmotivierten Pflegekr\u00e4fte sind am Limit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.360", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil das Personal fehlt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.360", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil es auf dem Arbeitsmarkt nicht vorhanden ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.800", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich werde Ihnen gleich schildern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.120", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie wir versuchen werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.440", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das zu \u00e4ndern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.880", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Einen Satz noch: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.200", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unserem hochmotivierten Pflegepersonal in ganz Deutschland, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.560", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das gerade arbeitet oder in der verdienten Pause ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.040", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "m\u00f6chte ich an dieser Stelle sagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "100.600", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es einen tollen Job macht"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "100.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.080", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und dass wir alles daf\u00fcr tun werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.360", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es in Zukunft nicht mehr so am Limit arbeiten muss, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.600", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie es dies bisher tut. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.400", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie gesagt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.280", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir brauchen dringend mehr Pflegekr\u00e4fte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.560", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sowohl im ambulanten als auch im station\u00e4ren Bereich als auch in den Krankenh\u00e4usern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.720", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie erreichen wir das? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.080", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ganz einfach: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.640", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00fcssen die Berufe im Pflegebereich attraktiver machen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.680", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "attraktiver gegen\u00fcber den Berufen in anderen Wirtschaftsbereichen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "131.400", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wir m\u00fcssen sie st\u00e4rken. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "131.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.800", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen bessere Rahmen- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.760", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Arbeitsbedingungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.560", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit es gelingt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "140.880", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wieder mehr junge Menschen in die Pflegeberufe zu bekommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "140.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.800", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sie zu begeistern und vor allen Dingen ein vorzeitiges Ausscheiden zu verhindern; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.360", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn es ist doch auch ein Problem, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.840", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Pflegekr\u00e4fte wegen ihrer \u00dcberbelastung zu kurz in ihrem Beruf arbeiten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.120", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das m\u00fcssen wir \u00e4ndern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.360", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Personalausstattung ist eine wichtige Rahmenbedingung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.880", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.640", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie sieht es denn aus? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.960", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich habe es eben schon gesagt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.280", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In meinem Bundesland Schleswig-Holstein werden von den Krankenh\u00e4usern mittlerweile schon Abwerbepr\u00e4mien gezahlt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.640", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit das Pflegepersonal von dem einen zum anderen Krankenhaus wechselt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.400", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daher\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.680", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich wiederhole es\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.800", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "brauchen wir ein Sofortprogramm f\u00fcr mehr Pflegekr\u00e4fte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.200", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das sofort greift und nicht erst in drei Jahren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.480", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn neue Pflegekr\u00e4fte ausgebildet sind."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.320", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Neben einer Ausbildungsoffensive, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.560", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die den Namen auch verdient, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.760", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wollen wir Anreize f\u00fcr eine bessere R\u00fcckkehr von Teil- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.720", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in Vollzeit. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.240", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen verbesserte M\u00f6glichkeiten zur Weiterqualifizierung von Pflegehelfern zu Pflegefachkr\u00e4ften, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.040", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die nat\u00fcrlich auch mehr verdienen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.360", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir brauchen eine st\u00e4rkere F\u00f6rderung familienfreundlicher Arbeitszeitmodelle\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.280", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in der Pflege arbeiten haupts\u00e4chlich Frauen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.560", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "man muss die Arbeitszeiten auch auf sie ausrichten\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.680", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wir brauchen eine bessere Gesundheitsvorsorge f\u00fcr die Besch\u00e4ftigten in diesen wichtigen Pflegeberufen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.560", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daneben brauchen wir eine Reduzierung des b\u00fcrokratischen Aufwandes; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.000", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.560", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hier bin ich ganz bei Ihnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.440", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "IT-Systeme unterst\u00fctzen das. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "232.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.680", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Pflegekr\u00e4fte wollen Zeit f\u00fcr ihre Patienten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "236.880", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ihre Pflegebed\u00fcrftigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.040", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "haben und nicht Zeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.240", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um zu dokumentieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.840", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der wichtigste Punkt ist aber\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.360", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist wirklich ganz wichtig\u00a0\u2013: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.240", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Pflegeberufe brauchen mehr gesellschaftliche Wertsch\u00e4tzung und W\u00fcrdigung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.360", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "253.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.760", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich finde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "253.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.320", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "da kann man ruhig applaudieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "259.360", 
   "id": "s000089", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil das \u00fcberparteilich ist."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "259.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.480", 
   "id": "s000090", 
   "language": "deu", 
